<HEADLINE>
<P>
SAN DIEGO SPOTLIGHT: SAN DIEGO ENTERTAINMENT BRIEFS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Three's Company and Dancers just received a $55,000 grant from Jewels of 
Charity, a national foundation with headquarters in Delaware. Part of the gift 
is earmarked to support the company's New York debut at the Merce Cunningham 
studio May 5-6. 
</P>
</TEXT>
